  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    This is the base class for anything that needs to move/act on the screen.
    Astronaut
    This is a sample actor that will use the keyboard input to move.

    This class controls the JPanel where the game logic and rendering happen.
    Bullet
    This is an example bullet class that extends the Actor class.
    GameRunner
    This is the main class that will run the game.
    SingleComponentAspectRatioKeeperLayout
    A Swing Layout that will shrink or enlarge keep the content of a container while keeping it's aspect ratio.
    Utility
    This is the Utility class used by the Java 2D Game.
